on the Southern African Development Community (SADC) Trade
Protocol, said he would use the opportunity to persuade his South
African counterpart to make a commitment.
</P>
<P>
It is prudent that the SACU agreement is signed before the SADC
Trade Protocol to pave the way for easy trade in the region, he
said, showing confidence that all issues would be ironed out soon.
 
