<HEADLINE> China's Anhui Sets Up First Private Venture Capital Company </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, June 19 (Xinhua) -- East China's Anhui province recently
set up a private venture capital company -- Hefei High-Tech
Venture Capital Company Ltd.
</P>
<P>
A local source said that the investment focus of the company
will be on telecommunications, software application, bio-
engineering and other related high-tech sectors.
</P>
<P>
First introduced in the 1980s, the concept of venture capital
is still new for many Chinese. Local experts have called for
measures to support the growing and expanding venture capital
market in China. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
