<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 19 (Xinhua) -- Beijing reported hazardous
pollution today, Shijiazhuang and Taiyuan in north China saw
slight air pollution, while very little air pollution was recorded
in Tianjin, Shenyang Hohhot, Nanjing, Hangzhou, Hefei, Yantai,
Wuhan, Changsha and Xi'an.
</P>
<P>
