<P>
"The working party report and the protocols of (Oman's )
membership will be adopted (by the WTO) on July 6," said Al Riyami,
who is heading Oman's WTO negotiating team.
</P>
<P>
Oman has launched several reforms in its bid for full WTO
membership, including lifting fees levied by import agents on
imported goods. (Oman-WTO) 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
