<HEADLINE> Facts &AMP; Figures: China's Exports to Germany in First 4 Months </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 19 (Xinhua) -- Following are the latest facts and
figures of China's major export commodities to Germany in the
first 4 months this year, provided by the General Administration
of Customs:
</P>
<P>
-- Machines, electronic goods, audiovisual equipment and
relevant parts and accessories: 915.976 million U.S. dollars.
